<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>E-mail simples</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #444444;
    }
    h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1em;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 0.5em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>E-mail Enviado do Site - <strong>{{host}}</strong></p>
    <p>Ol√°,</p>
    <p>Este e-mail foi enviado por <strong>{{from}}</strong> em <strong>{{date}}</strong>.</p>
    <p><strong>Assunto:</strong> {{subject}}</p>
    <p><strong>Mensagem:</strong> {{text}}</p>
    <br>
    <h4>Obrigado, Fabi Sacramento Makeup - Equipe de Tecnologia</h4>
  </div>
</body>
</html>